{"tid":396114,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"灰到喊，係香港到底點先算係一個人？","createTime":"2017-09-11T11:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T02:11:09.000Z","uid":22019,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc5fcd51f7e59c7bfd62875503ff5d4785d2706f","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:51:18.000Z","msg":"三十幾歲人，無車無樓無事業<br />\n細細個父母叫努力讀書<br />\n但無人教你要揀咩科<br />\n自己半工讀完成大學<br />\n出黎打份文職，唔係專科無特別技能<br />\n同年紀啲朋友，讀唔成書既做幾年野就嫁人<br />\n讀得成既就做專業人士/公務員<br />\n嫁左人既就等老公買樓做少奶<br />\n搵到錢既就買層私樓娶老婆<br />\n個個屋企都請工人做家務<br />\n<br />\n我唔知香港地有幾多人有父幹<br />\n不過係我身邊就好多<br />\n再唔係就搵到個老公特別叻特別有錢<br />\n私樓一開新盤就去抽，我連首置都無資格<br />\n<br />\n我唔想怨天尤人，但我都唔知點做<br />\n自問已經好努力，但好似永遠都停滯不前<br />\n<br />\n仔又唔敢生<br />\n首期又儲唔到<br />\n移民又無錢<br />\n<br />\n每日每月就係返工放工交租拖地洗衫<br />\n好想知係香港到底有無第二種生存模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05fe1dfe08e00658feec141bc6aebad97ef643d0","tid":396114,"uid":75372,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:52:49.000Z","msg":"學習投資"},{"pid":"92888594bcc56bd421f058222c8bf91b2620ad76","tid":396114,"uid":25128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:53:19.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c3d2d8f85b302447792fbfc4f95c32f74b23b5","tid":396114,"uid":59192,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"女既仲有嫁人既機會<br />\n男既就係咁先"},{"pid":"e4f049f180cf513eb25e1f7c782da77f759847a6","tid":396114,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"點解廿幾個時唔把握機會"},{"pid":"6fdc52dd4600609e96e5f8e3f3cdc64b2e787609","tid":396114,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:59:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e4e84ee5263dc07239c95d747bf3aede757ebfb","tid":396114,"uid":121349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"搵得唔多真係唔好生仔，唔只累左佢，仲累埋自己，生完就要勞碌一世"},{"pid":"e007025ea0af9dd3c36dde31348f461ccb3ad085","tid":396114,"uid":121349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:29:39.000Z","msg":"樓主男定女"},{"pid":"9f00e36d829d70031a7dcd2be3ad0a6e86e9d79f","tid":396114,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:34:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主男定女</blockquote><br />\n佢講d野係女性角度,但我覺得佢係男<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a7633d79cf4e9396bef285cabe37b5c68beab8","tid":396114,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"樓主kongu?"},{"pid":"d97204f815f820cd80110958be3fefb214cc1ec3","tid":396114,"uid":103979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三十幾歲人，無車無樓無事業<br />\n細細個父母叫努力讀書<br />\n但無人教你要揀咩科<br />\n自己半工讀完成大學<br />\n出黎打份文職，唔係專科無特別技能<br />\n同年紀啲朋友，讀唔成書既做幾年野就嫁人<br />\n讀得成既就做專業人士/公務員<br />\n嫁左人既就等老公買樓做少奶<br />\n搵到錢既就買層私樓娶老婆<br />\n個個屋企都請工人做家務<br />\n<br />\n我唔知香港地有幾多人有父幹<br />\n不過係我身邊就好多<br />\n再唔係就搵到個老公特別叻特別有錢<br />\n私樓一開新盤就去抽，我連首置都無資格<br />\n<br />\n我唔想怨天尤人，但我都唔知點做<br />\n自問已經好努力，但好似永遠都停滯不前<br />\n<br />\n仔又唔敢生<br />\n首期又儲唔到<br />\n移民又無錢<br />\n<br />\n每日每月就係返工放工交租拖地洗衫<br />\n好想知係香港到底有無第二種生存模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n相同感覺，以前會好肯定話唔會做樓奴，拎啲錢去旅行好過。<br />\n但越黎越大個就發覺冇樓真係好難組織到家庭，又會俾啲親朋問你買樓未。搞到而家唔 敢洗錢死儲爛儲。但都係買唔到&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c6189d0709626f54518beafd684e73db89caf8","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學習投資</blockquote><br />\n以前都試過 但真係無乜天份<br />\n本身對數字白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecface1c94cf45517bf7ab66d44b699fcde5d787","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女既仲有嫁人既機會<br />\n男既就係咁先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全明白<br />\n我同另一半都係一樣<br />\n唔會怪佢<br />\n不過覺得大家都無乜出路"},{"pid":"10f5ba90d85fc6ab6babff08d53c2aa05391e8c4","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:54:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解廿幾個時唔把握機會</blockquote><br />\n點解？我都想知<br />\n細個白白痴痴 邊知咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連邊個係機會都唔知"},{"pid":"bf0bc89d80f8e9712f4361f698ce6d214f64212c","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:55:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無老豆老母幫/老豆老母廢<br />\n<br />\n=輸左<br />\n<br />\n除非做到醫生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好唔想承認 但係真<br />\n由細到大唔想靠人<br />\n乜都自己做自己受<br />\n結果係俾人笑傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140dccded6ffdd1a7bfb7fac1a1c65c3834da1cd","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主男定女</blockquote><br />\n佢講d野係女性角度,但我覺得佢係男<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n女，嫁左"},{"pid":"8de13c9ddacd34bad66655cfb2fc0092ccd69835","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主kongu?</blockquote><br />\n唔係，理大"},{"pid":"865241e36956530dc83e602e9aca16e4c29a4864","tid":396114,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:56:56.000Z","msg":"諗個方法上左公屋先<br />\n然後上網搵洋腸食，30對佢黎講係廿幾<br />\n諗一個適合自己既計劃，人人條路都唔同，無得羨慕人哋<br />\n我夠羨慕我老豆有父幹+兄弟姊妹幹，但佢可以係我十八歲前蝕哂幾層港島樓我都無辦法，唯有行plan b<br />\n你可能後生有計劃過，但計劃趕唔上變化，咁你就要改。條路自己既，你羨慕人既同時人地已經走左好遠"},{"pid":"fea2f962c74b528179a855f907ac885c8796054a","tid":396114,"uid":33874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:57:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗個方法上左公屋先<br />\n<del>然後上網搵洋腸食，30對佢黎講係廿幾</del><br />\n諗一個適合自己既計劃，人人條路都唔同，無得羨慕人哋<br />\n我夠羨慕我老豆有父幹+兄弟姊妹幹，但佢可以係我十八歲前蝕哂幾層港島樓我都無辦法，唯有行plan b<br />\n你可能後生有計劃過，但計劃趕唔上變化，咁你就要改。條路自己既，你羨慕人既同時人地已經走左好遠</blockquote><br />\nsor，打既時候唔知已婚"},{"pid":"b65cc4fcf4b7568c2b3bebfe783175391f5f0196","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三十幾歲人，無車無樓無事業<br />\n細細個父母叫努力讀書<br />\n但無人教你要揀咩科<br />\n自己半工讀完成大學<br />\n出黎打份文職，唔係專科無特別技能<br />\n同年紀啲朋友，讀唔成書既做幾年野就嫁人<br />\n讀得成既就做專業人士/公務員<br />\n嫁左人既就等老公買樓做少奶<br />\n搵到錢既就買層私樓娶老婆<br />\n個個屋企都請工人做家務<br />\n<br />\n我唔知香港地有幾多人有父幹<br />\n不過係我身邊就好多<br />\n再唔係就搵到個老公特別叻特別有錢<br />\n私樓一開新盤就去抽，我連首置都無資格<br />\n<br />\n我唔想怨天尤人，但我都唔知點做<br />\n自問已經好努力，但好似永遠都停滯不前<br />\n<br />\n仔又唔敢生<br />\n首期又儲唔到<br />\n移民又無錢<br />\n<br />\n每日每月就係返工放工交租拖地洗衫<br />\n好想知係香港到底有無第二種生存模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n相同感覺，以前會好肯定話唔會做樓奴，拎啲錢去旅行好過。<br />\n但越黎越大個就發覺冇樓真係好難組織到家庭，又會俾啲親朋問你買樓未。搞到而家唔 敢洗錢死儲爛儲。但都係買唔到&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係，以前覺得去睇下世界好重要，唔想有野綁住自己。而家身邊個個定哂，自己仲為緊兩餐奔波，唔知自己做乜，覺得自己好廢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1084a46c0b9e2489b5fa6570cbf4db24f3e51a","tid":396114,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:59:58.000Z","msg":"家庭月入有幾多?"},{"pid":"03a9f87d26a1998ce0917e1e28cde3b2fbea3841","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗個方法上左公屋先<br />\n<del>然後上網搵洋腸食，30對佢黎講係廿幾</del><br />\n諗一個適合自己既計劃，人人條路都唔同，無得羨慕人哋<br />\n我夠羨慕我老豆有父幹+兄弟姊妹幹，但佢可以係我十八歲前蝕哂幾層港島樓我都無辦法，唯有行plan b<br />\n你可能後生有計劃過，但計劃趕唔上變化，咁你就要改。條路自己既，你羨慕人既同時人地已經走左好遠</blockquote><br />\nsor，打既時候唔知已婚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我人生既計劃只係想自己活得開心，可以養到父母，唔使餐搵餐食餐餐清，有閒錢去下旅行。而家一直都行緊，只係路途遙遠，過程死板，睇唔到個盡頭。<br />\n<br />\n我都明白心態係由自己改變<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSor 一時感慨"},{"pid":"e468de6bc5ac75195b1c58b41beba30187ed62b8","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>家庭月入有幾多?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未夠資格申請首置<br />\n又抽唔到居屋"},{"pid":"940497ea9830041a09564a421ecad8dac591f07f","tid":396114,"uid":40536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:02:28.000Z","msg":"23歲揮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8b473557e99105f89d635c890e1b098bb4bde7","tid":396114,"uid":102322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"起碼身上無重擔<br />\n又揾到個自己鍾意既人先<br />\n有無諗過點解扎鐵咁辛苦都有3x歲既人入行?<br />\n其中一個原因係佢地想揾機會,<br />\n想突破個困境<br />\n好多野就係靠毅力拼出黎<br />\n唔係諗下就會有...<br />\n邊個唔知文職舒服呢"},{"pid":"c8c90244f8afee511ed53f7e5cbb85df47e96993","tid":396114,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"唔只係香港既"},{"pid":"6cf01b9f73a6ef476d32c20f076bfe2db5928546","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起碼身上無重擔<br />\n又揾到個自己鍾意既人先<br />\n有無諗過點解扎鐵咁辛苦都有3x歲既人入行?<br />\n其中一個原因係佢地想揾機會,<br />\n想突破個困境<br />\n好多野就係靠毅力拼出黎<br />\n唔係諗下就會有...<br />\n邊個唔知文職舒服呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想搵機會<br />\n之前試過幾次轉換環境但唔成功<br />\n不過愈大愈怕無糧出<br />\n始終要交租要生活<br />\n做開果行離開得耐就搵唔返果個人工"},{"pid":"ab14a1c6bd90999e1b7e718517272fa6487c23d2","tid":396114,"uid":81569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:19:51.000Z","msg":"27歲<br />\n中五畢業<br />\n公屋仔<br />\n做倉務  月入不足14000<br />\n樣衰，矮，少肥<br />\n從來都溝唔到女<br />\n比家人，同事，上司，朋友睇唔起<br />\n<br />\n我都未放棄人生，你嘈咩"},{"pid":"e9630fbfbaf5b65ea300e27110faa88e99ea689e","tid":396114,"uid":102322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>起碼身上無重擔<br />\n又揾到個自己鍾意既人先<br />\n有無諗過點解扎鐵咁辛苦都有3x歲既人入行?<br />\n其中一個原因係佢地想揾機會,<br />\n想突破個困境<br />\n好多野就係靠毅力拼出黎<br />\n唔係諗下就會有...<br />\n邊個唔知文職舒服呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想搵機會<br />\n之前試過幾次轉換環境但唔成功<br />\n不過愈大愈怕無糧出<br />\n始終要交租要生活<br />\n做開果行離開得耐就搵唔返果個人工</blockquote><br />\n宜家揾幾多?"},{"pid":"b4893f34adcbe5d3bbae9c225b80411a7af43592","tid":396114,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>27歲<br />\n中五畢業<br />\n公屋仔<br />\n做倉務  月入不足14000<br />\n樣衰，矮，少肥<br />\n從來都溝唔到女<br />\n比家人，同事，上司，朋友睇唔起<br />\n<br />\n我都未放棄人生，你嘈咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n修羅模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfb865c3c8d943a259c9c4223683f7ca404ec9f","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:25:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>27歲<br />\n中五畢業<br />\n公屋仔<br />\n做倉務  月入不足14000<br />\n樣衰，矮，少肥<br />\n從來都溝唔到女<br />\n比家人，同事，上司，朋友睇唔起<br />\n<br />\n我都未放棄人生，你嘈咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講下野都唔得？<br />\n<br />\n我都未放棄人生<br />\n想搵人傾下計姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bb36e6662d61518d538eef43def77411905e25","tid":396114,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>27歲<br />\n中五畢業<br />\n公屋仔<br />\n做倉務  月入不足14000<br />\n樣衰，矮，少肥<br />\n從來都溝唔到女<br />\n比家人，同事，上司，朋友睇唔起<br />\n<br />\n我都未放棄人生，你嘈咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講下野都唔得？<br />\n<br />\n我都未放棄人生<br />\n想搵人傾下計姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我仍然覺得自己有一日會成功<br />\n你都得"},{"pid":"7b9899d7c78cbd914f2a0b913f83ac6fa9f50dcc","tid":396114,"uid":138169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:46:50.000Z","msg":"如果你結左婚，又唔敢生仔，可以考慮養隻狗仔，你既生活會有趣好多...出去放狗已經係一種放鬆既活動<br />\n<br />\n另外至少你有個老公可以同你分擔分享，好過好多嫁唔出又皺皮...果d 仲急仲無奈<br />\n<br />\n香港問題主要來自工時過長，租金太高，幻想下...只要每日工時縮到7小時，放工仲見到陽光，五天工作，收入同依家一樣，放假就同老公去郊遊下，帶埋狗仔...識下新朋友，傾下養狗經，咁其實都幾寫意...<br />\n<br />\n我明你感受，因為我同你一樣，覺得身邊d 朋友好多都已經生活得好好，上晒岸咁，就算見面、活動...好似都唔同層次...佢地個個講買樓，講車講物質，就顯得自己好似更廢...所以有時寧願唔見...<br />\n<br />\n但人係群體動物，無左可以交流既朋友，慢慢就會覺得生活好枯燥...所以，建議你可以養隻狗仔先，個人會減壓d, 慢慢就會識多d 新朋友，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb5ac0804eefbc52475dce749af37b8c1707ec9","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:25:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你結左婚，又唔敢生仔，可以考慮養隻狗仔，你既生活會有趣好多...出去放狗已經係一種放鬆既活動<br />\n<br />\n另外至少你有個老公可以同你分擔分享，好過好多嫁唔出又皺皮...果d 仲急仲無奈<br />\n<br />\n香港問題主要來自工時過長，租金太高，幻想下...只要每日工時縮到7小時，放工仲見到陽光，五天工作，收入同依家一樣，放假就同老公去郊遊下，帶埋狗仔...識下新朋友，傾下養狗經，咁其實都幾寫意...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我明你感受，因為我同你一樣，覺得身邊d 朋友好多都已經生活得好好，上晒岸咁，就算見面、活動...好似都唔同層次...佢地個個講買樓，講車講物質，就顯得自己好似更廢...所以有時寧願唔見...</span><br />\n<br />\n但人係群體動物，無左可以交流既朋友，慢慢就會覺得生活好枯燥...所以，建議你可以養隻狗仔先，個人會減壓d, 慢慢就會識多d 新朋友，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係咁啦，圍住身邊都係呢啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時覺得好累 好似抖唔到氣咁<br />\n<br />\n我有狗仔架 不過帶佢地出去車費好金，所以唔可以每個星期出。身邊啲朋友就會問，做乜唔買架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知點解今日特別感觸。<br />\n我會加油，大家都係。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c874979d4b69de7732cf105609a24e77daf6bef","tid":396114,"uid":145761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:45:20.000Z","msg":"香港人的悲歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04075461347795cb0afe60e7602d26a8e62f9818","tid":396114,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:46:04.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"dfc2b5f7d3837808135ca097ab27703098bcd5fe","tid":396114,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"後生唔做幾年雞搵快錢買樓揸手<br />\n家下你想做都搵唔到幾多<br />\n咁就一世架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915305327ea46bd8da7090d98e29a8f4bebf48ef","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>後生唔做幾年雞搵快錢買樓揸手<br />\n家下你想做都搵唔到幾多<br />\n咁就一世架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後生唔要愛情，日日化行妝去溝個富二代<br />\n家下就幾層豪宅揸手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲使返工捱騾仔咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54403b8067ad3ce53266d50dceba02ff3d3b5f57","tid":396114,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:13:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗個方法上左公屋先<br />\n<del>然後上網搵洋腸食，30對佢黎講係廿幾</del><br />\n諗一個適合自己既計劃，人人條路都唔同，無得羨慕人哋<br />\n我夠羨慕我老豆有父幹+兄弟姊妹幹，但佢可以係我十八歲前蝕哂幾層港島樓我都無辦法，唯有行plan b<br />\n你可能後生有計劃過，但計劃趕唔上變化，咁你就要改。條路自己既，你羨慕人既同時人地已經走左好遠</blockquote><br />\nsor，打既時候唔知已婚</blockquote><br />\n屌 睇到我笑撚左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b459fa3f7bf9bda333cd9f317b0cbe0ed6ed6c5a","tid":396114,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:13:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>後生唔做幾年雞搵快錢買樓揸手<br />\n家下你想做都搵唔到幾多<br />\n咁就一世架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後生唔要愛情，日日化行妝去溝個富二代<br />\n家下就幾層豪宅揸手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲使返工捱騾仔咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n知你又唔做<br />\n搞到家下咁"},{"pid":"2122f5d6801aec031667068bfe8979f0fc807076","tid":396114,"uid":22019,"like":0,"dislike":